<br>
Suddenly, the door opened and Hippolyte looked up.  Quickly standing in front of Alexiares, believing it would be one of the Roman men.  But, it was Elektra. <br>
<br>
&quot;What a sight for sore eyes,&quot; Hippolyte laughed. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

"We ride tonight!  With the strength that Hera has given
us-- and the strength that we have _earned_ for ourselves!  Take
what you need, but be quick.  Stay only until the sound of horn.
